#CHIP AY8910
#CLOCK 1789773

; AY8910 (General Instrument AY-3-8910) Wavetable Test
;
; The AY8910 has square wave generators that can be configured to produce
; different duty cycles and waveforms.
;
; Tests:
; - Square waves at various duty cycles
; - Noise channel (LFSR)
; - Combined tone and noise

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Tone channel 1: 50% duty cycle (square wave)
c4 . . .

; Tone channel 2: 25% duty cycle
d4 . . .

; Tone channel 3: 12.5% duty cycle (pulse)
e4 . . .

r4

; All 3 tone channels together
c4 & d4 & e4 .

r4

; Noise channel test (perussive sounds)
; Using low notes to trigger noise
c2 . d2 . e2 .

r4

; Combined tone and noise
c4 & c2 .

r2

#END
